%h2
  Hello, #{@resource.email}
%p
  You were invited to become a member of organization on the web-page spacex.com.ua
  
%h1
  = link_to t("devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept"), accept_invitation_url(@resource, invitation_token: @token)
  - if @resource.invitation_due_at
    = t("devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept_until", due_date: l(@resource.invitation_due_at, format: :'devise.mailer.invitation_instructions.accept_until_format'))

%p
  If you don't want to accept the invitation, please ignore this email. Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.
